<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="glare-n">glare <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡleə(r)/    美 /ɡler/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[常用单数] 刺眼的强光：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Because the South Pole is a high altitude site, the glare of the sunlight here is very intense.
由于南极位于高纬度地区，所以这里日光极为耀眼。</p><footer>外研⑧ – 1</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(长久的) 瞪眼；怒视：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>look at sb with a glare
怒视某人</p></div></div>